<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">No information exists on fire characteristics for the alliance, but the ecology of its character species suggests that the regime may be similar to <i>Lotus scoparius</i>. Stands have relatively low shrub cover and high herbaceous cover. Seeds of the character species form a seed bank and they germinate after fire or other disturbance.</div>
